Items.c: <[>算了,他雖然想取我性命,我卻不想害他。反正我提醒他有陷阱,聽不聽在於他。<]>
Items.mt: <[>Never mind, although he wants to take my life, I don't want to harm him. Anyway, I warned him of the trap, and it was up to him to listen or not. <]>
